
Step 1: first clone this repository to your local machine using the following command one by one :

git clone https://github.com/sami4346/Tools_Backend.git
cd Tools_Backend
npm install
npm install cors
npm install mongodb
npm install mongoose
npm install dotenv
npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite


Step 2: Create a new file called .env in the root directory of your project and add 

MONGO_URI = link from mongodb cluster
DB_USER = user name from mongodb cluster
DB_PASS = user password from mongodb cluster

